<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Validation OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #020817;
            color: #F8FAFC;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p, .email-body, .email-footer {
            color: #F8FAFC !important; /* Forcer la couleur */
        }

        span {
            color: #F8FAFC !important; /* Forcer la couleur */
        }

        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #1B202E;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(186, 186, 186, 0.5);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .email-header {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(186, 186, 186, 0.5);
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* OTP container with equal spacing */
        .otp-container {
            display: table;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        

        .otp-box {
            display: inline;
            padding: 11px 20px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            background-color: #0f1523;
            border: 1px solid rgba(186, 186, 186, 0.5);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #F8FAFC;
            text-align: center;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 8px 5px;
        }

        .email-footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9B87F5;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container" style="width: 100%; max-width: 500px;">
        <div class="email-header"><span>ðŸ”‘ Activation de votre compte cryptomonnaie</span></div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Bonjour,</p>
            <p>Pour activer votre compte, veuillez utiliser le code OTP suivant :</p>
            <div class="otp-container">
                {% for digit in pinCode %}
                    <div class="otp-box">{{ digit }}</div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>            

            <p>Ce code est valable pendant {{ duration }}. Si vous n'avez pas demandÃ© cette activation, veuillez ignorer cet email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>Cordialement, l'Ã©quipe de Cryptomonnaie</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>